《'''錫瓦斯'''》（''Sivas''） 是一部2014年[[Kaan_Mujdeci|Kaan Mujdeci]]执导的[[土耳其|土耳其]]剧情片，入选[[第71届威尼斯影展|第71届威尼斯影展]]主竞赛片<ref name="Venice">{{cite web |url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/71st-festival/line-up/off-sel/venezia71/ |title=International competition of feature films |accessdate=24 July 2014 |work=Venice |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006083927/http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/71st-festival/line-up/off-sel/venezia71/ |archivedate=2014-10-06}}</ref><ref name="Deadline">{{cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/07/venice-film-festival-lineup-2014-movie-list/ |title=Venice Film Festival Lineup Announced |accessdate=24 July 2014 |work=Deadline |archive-date=2014-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140728233935/http://www.deadline.com/2014/07/venice-film-festival-lineup-2014-movie-list/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并收获评委会特别奖<ref >{{cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/14/0907/10/A5HJ27LD00034U9K.html |language= |title=第71届威尼斯国际电影节 完整获奖名单 |publisher=网易娱乐 |date=2014-09-07 |accessdate= |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305024418/http://ent.163.com/14/0907/10/A5HJ27LD00034U9K.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

